        "heading": "Forty years in the craft. Then something more personal",
        "body_text": "<p>Kyle has been working with leather, paper, and binding techniques for over forty years. What started as a bookbinding trade grew into a deep understanding of materials, craftsmanship, and the kind of work that lasts.</p><p>When he and Tracy started Treasured Moments Photos, the goal was simple: take that same care and apply it to something personal. Every piece we make is assembled by hand in our South Jordan, Utah workshop using UV-printed images on real wood and vegan leather — built to hold up, not just look good on a shelf.</p>",
